nk ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-thiep-moi-khai-truong.html\/#Vai_tro_cua_thiep_moi_khai_truong\" title=\"Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng\">Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-thiep-moi-khai-truong.html\/#Xu_huong_thiet_ke_thiep_moi_le_khai_truong\" title=\"Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi l\u1ec5 khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng\">Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi l\u1ec5 khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-thiep-moi-khai-truong.html\/#Dich_vu_thiet_ke_thiep_moi_tai_A_Chau_Media\" title=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi t\u1ea1i \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi t\u1ea1i \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-thiep-moi-khai-truong.html\/#Quy_trinh_dich_vu_thiet_ke_thiep_moi\" title=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi\">Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-thiep-moi-khai-truong.html\/#Nam_diem_khac_biet_tai_A_Chau_Media\" title=\"N\u0103m \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media\">N\u0103m \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\r\n<p><em>Thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi l\u00e0 \u1ea5n ph\u1ea9m r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, trao g\u1eedi thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1 tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi. M\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m<strong> thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb9p, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m n\u01a1i kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi t\u1eeb c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. <strong>L\u1ec5 khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/strong> l\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 quan tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p. Bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u may m\u1eafn cho c\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh kinh doanh v\u1ec1 sau \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cthu\u1eadn bu\u1ed3m xu\u00f4i gi\u00f3\u201d. Trong kinh doanh m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m <strong>thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1eb9p<\/strong> v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c, b\u1ea1n h\u00e0ng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty r\u1ea5t ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 in thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/em><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-online.html\/\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4598\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/1200-529598073-orient-invitation-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng\" width=\"850\" height=\"851\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/1200-529598073-orient-invitation-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/1200-529598073-orient-invitation-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/1200-529598073-orient-invitation-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/1200-529598073-orient-invitation-768x769.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/1200-529598073-orient-invitation.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Vai_tro_cua_thiep_moi_khai_truong\"><\/span><strong>Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc <strong>thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin c\u00f2n n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ty h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9, thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c<strong> thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f4ng ty<\/strong>\u00a0th\u1eddi trang, c\u00f4ng ty qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng sang tr\u1ecdng <\/strong>b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 doanh nghi\u1ec7p mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c.<\/li>\r\n<li>Thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p gi\u00fap cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n ngay t\u1eeb l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u<\/li>\r\n<li>Thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a bu\u1ed5i ti\u1ec7c, gi\u00fap cho kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi th\u1ea5y n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p. C\u1ea3 m\u1eb7t qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh l\u1eabn c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4601\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/invitation-card-luxury-gold-template-design-vector-22699527-1.jpg\" alt=\"thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi\" width=\"850\" height=\"655\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/invitation-card-luxury-gold-template-design-vector-22699527-1.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/invitation-card-luxury-gold-template-design-vector-22699527-1-300x231.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/invitation-card-luxury-gold-template-design-vector-22699527-1-768x591.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Xu_huong_thiet_ke_thiep_moi_le_khai_truong\"><\/span><strong>Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi l\u1ec5 khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i <strong>thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/strong> kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ec7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7n nay:<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ec7p th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o. T\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5.<\/li>\r\n<li>B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c <strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi<\/strong>\u00a0 n\u00ean \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u00f3a c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft th\u1eeba. T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p mu\u1ed1n truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i<\/li>\r\n<li>M\u00e0u s\u1eafc h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh linh ho\u1ea1t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi logo doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n. Hai y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9. Theo c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia t\u1ed1i \u0111a ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng 3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc tr\u00ean t\u1ea5m thi\u1ec7p khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/li>\r\n<li>Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u gi\u1ea5y in thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi sang tr\u1ecdng: qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5y m\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 in thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi. Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u gi\u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00ec m\u1edbi t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng cho b\u1ed9 thi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea5y h\u1ee3p l\u00fd t\u1eeb 300gsm tr\u1edf l\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ed9 thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu.html\/\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dich_vu_thiet_ke_thiep_moi_tai_A_Chau_Media\"><\/span><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi t\u1ea1i \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/strong> chi ti\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh r\u00f5 n\u00e9t theo \u0111\u00fang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch<\/li>\r\n<li><strong>M\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi<\/strong> \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/li>\r\n<li>H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c file \u1ea3nh m\u00e1y t\u00ednh, file\u00a0vector\u00a0d\u00f9ng cho in \u1ea5n. \u0110\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng file c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft:\u00a0GIF, JPG, PSD, EPS<\/li>\r\n<li>C\u1ea9m nang h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn, b\u1ea3n thuy\u1ebft minh \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf<\/li>\r\n<li>Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 to\u00e0n quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf<\/li>\r\n<li>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n\u00a0chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p\u00a0v\u1ec1 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4603\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/luxury-invitation-card-in-vintage-style-vector-22699167.jpg\" alt=\"thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi l\u1ec5 khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng\" width=\"850\" height=\"590\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/luxury-invitation-card-in-vintage-style-vector-22699167.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/luxury-invitation-card-in-vintage-style-vector-22699167-300x208.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/luxury-invitation-card-in-vintage-style-vector-22699167-768x533.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_dich_vu_thiet_ke_thiep_moi\"><\/span><strong>Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/li>\r\n<li>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: K\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/li>\r\n<li>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: L\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng<\/li>\r\n<li>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf<\/li>\r\n<li>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: B\u00e0n giao v\u00e0 nghi\u1ec7m thu<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-website-wordpress.html\/\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nam_diem_khac_biet_tai_A_Chau_Media\"><\/span><strong>N\u0103m \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Cam k\u1ebft \u0111\u00fang h\u1eb9n: mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng<\/li>\r\n<li>Cam k\u1ebft l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c: thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo \u0111\u00fang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/li>\r\n<li>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed: c\u00e1c g\u00f3i d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/li>\r\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i: h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda \u0111\u1ebfn khi n\u00e0o kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng nh\u1ea5t<\/li>\r\n<li>Xu\u1ea5t VAT \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7: t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i<strong> \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong> \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t VAT theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Thi\u1ebft 